results.lead_paragraph: MOST people advised my wife and me to put off a European bicycling trip until our children, age 2 and 5, were grown, but we were too impatient to wait for our 2-year-old to get out of diapers. As it was, the trip turned out to be a study in contrasts, but we will never forget the good part and we will be laughing at the bad part for years.

results.lead_paragraph: Martin Caidin, whose books go into orbit with the speed of the space vehicles he writes about, will have his first novel launched by Dutton on March 31.
